og.description: What blows my mind is that Republicans were the genesis of both what has become Obama Care (the Affordable Care Act) and Title X (Federal Support For Birth Control). President Richard Nixon, a staunch Republican, supported the Family Planning Act (Title X). Ironically, the same party now strives to demolish both.
